title: Republicans falling flat at Benghazi hearing, Hillary Clinton appears unscathed
text: Hillary Clinton finally found herself in front of members of the Benghazi Select Committee on Thursday and the results were as expected. Despite their best efforts, the Republican dominated committee has offered very little in the form of new information, as the former Secretary of State wiggled her way through much of the day looking the same as she did in the months prior. Photo by Alex Wong/Getty Images
